<section id="offering" class="py-24 px-8 bg-navy text-ivory">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold mb-6">
        How it works
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Process Steps -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-16">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gold/20 border border-gold/30 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">1. Onboarding call</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-ivory/70">You share your watchlist—portfolio companies, target accounts, key sectors. We discuss what triggers matter most. Takes 15 minutes.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gold/20 border border-gold/30 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.066 2.573c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573 1.066c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066-2.573c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"/>
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">2. Build</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-ivory/70">We configure the monitoring, test the filters, and deliver your first sample brief for review. Takes 2–3 days.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gold/20 border border-gold/30 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">3. Free week starts</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-ivory/70">Briefs arrive daily or weekly (your choice). See what you've been missing. Adjust the watchlist anytime.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gold/20 border border-gold/30 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">4. You decide</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-ivory/70">If it's valuable, continue. If not, walk away—no payment, no awkwardness.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Pricing -->
    <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-10">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">Week 1: Free trial</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-ivory/80 leading-relaxed">
            We build your custom monitoring setup and deliver one week of news briefs. No payment required.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">After that: You decide</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-ivory/80 leading-relaxed">
            If it's valuable, continue for <span class="text-gold font-semibold">€1,500</span> (one-time build fee) + <span class="text-gold font-semibold">€500/month</span> for managed monitoring. If not, no hard feelings.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
